DISCLAIMER: We do not, in any way, promote or glorify cruel acts committed by any communist state. Communism, in Marxist theory does not condone injustice or barbaric persecution of humankind.

Once again, this app is for both educational and entertainment purposes (meme app), and we DO NOT glorify past, unfortunate events perpetrated by extremist leaders.

Spread communist USSR vibes with your friends today!

Key features:
• Send any USSR communist sound you like to your friends
• Add button widgets on your home screen with your favorite line
• Set any sound as a notification or ringtone
• Choose between dark and light themes

You can find many communist songs such as:
- Moskau
- The Internationale
- Kalinka
- Rasputin
- Katyusha
- and much more!

The sounds have been optimized for the best listening experience. Your ringtone and alarm communism sounds will be louder and more effective!
descriptionShort: Use this button to listen to the soviet USSR anthems with the press of a button!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: App has been completely rewritten. Enjoy!
